{"tid":2068511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[膠國奇聞] 一男子坐左上條魚倒入左後眼","createTime":"2020-06-17T17:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T18:10:03.000Z","uid":164494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c16c7f4fc4fed84f2596cbe400b862b241978ca8","tid":2068511,"uid":164494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T17:42:02.000Z","msg":"廣東肇慶一名男子肚痛到醫院就診，自稱「不小心坐到魚上了」，而醫生進行開腹手術後，發現裡面有一整條「非洲鯽魚」（羅菲魚），取出後已經腐爛發臭，在場的醫護人員都忍不住嘔吐。<br />\n<br />\n該男子6月2日上午因為腹痛去醫院就診，但是在醫生問具體什麼位置疼痛，該男子卻支支吾吾說不出個所以，但也許是疼痛太厲害了，男子低聲說到，因為自己不小心坐到了一條非洲鯽魚身上，導致其進入了自己的直腸。<br />\n<br />\n因為事情緊急，醫生馬上安排其拍X光片查看具體情況，從拍出來的影像可以明顯看到有一條完整的魚在男子體內，並且魚頭最寬處已達30.5mm了，隨後醫生立馬安排手術將魚從男子體內取出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1790983/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%82%9B%E9%96%80%E5%85%A7%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E6%95%B4%E6%A2%9D%E9%AD%9A-%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83%E5%9D%90%E5%88%B0%E9%AD%9A%E4%B8%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1790983%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%2582%259B%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%2585%25A7%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%2595%25B4%25E6%25A2%259D%25E9%25AD%259A-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%259D%2590%25E5%2588%25B0%25E9%25AD%259A%25E4%25B8%258A&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4waooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=b6f85bd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1790983%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%2582%259B%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%2585%25A7%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%2595%25B4%25E6%25A2%259D%25E9%25AD%259A-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%259D%2590%25E5%2588%25B0%25E9%25AD%259A%25E4%25B8%258A&h=7b28d39a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1790983/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%82%9B%E9%96%80%E5%85%A7%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E6%95%B4%E6%A2%9D%E9%AD%9A-%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83%E5%9D%90%E5%88%B0%E9%AD%9A%E4%B8%8A</a>"},{"pid":"390a353133b7222e2bc359083087d3618daa154a","tid":2068511,"uid":237970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T17:46:30.000Z","msg":"女人挽黃鱔 男人挽鯽魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1450360821fc67d6244dabe80ff5a22ac8d6d407","tid":2068511,"uid":109670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T18:10:03.000Z","msg":"坐咗幾耐"}]}